0.10.name: wordpress/ajaxchat
0.10.description: Provides a simple chat system integrated into your blog. It adds a bar with a height of 20 pixels across the bottom of the browser's viewport. The div for the bar is position:fixed. This means that older browsers, Internet Explorer 6, for instance, may not display the bar at all. I may create a work-around for IE6 in the future. This plug-in is in the early stages of development (as of 2010-06-01). Any ideas/suggestions/bugs can be submitted to me via http://paydensutherland.com.
